<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1289789-disclaimer-do-not-read-unless-you-have">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[**Disclaimer do not read unless you have finished the novel** <br /><br />Why was it so imperative to Mick that David was acquitted for the murder? Wouldn't it have been smarter to convict someone else for the crime? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
