              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10580487855000684852">This is a legal procedural set in Philadelphia. As a Philly local I love books set in Philly. Love them. And the first 50% of this book had me absolutely charmed. It was an excellent mystery and Philly was well featured. when the twist in the tale came I was stunned. Stunned. STUNNED. And then annoyed.<br/><br/>So 4 stars rather than 5. I still plan on reading the next book by the author.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


